Zhongxin Fruits might have a move sooner than later. Can watch for this one. Trading Game plan: Cup & Handle rally  test year high of $0.037 and break out into 4 series. However  at the final second  they removed 50 lots sell Q 34 and closed it $0.035. This shows the BBs intention for higher prices with such control . If trade  do have a stop loss plan too. Good luck to all vested.
